7645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"到底數學要去到咩level先睇得明EFE啲term<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc304acb8ba961daf54e23c9536b734296f4eb0","tid":788781,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我岩岩先google 左bound system<br />\nbound system係expansion之下會keep relative position 係因為effect of gravity&gt;expansion<br />\n但expansion of universe 一個key point係metric expension<br />\n即係&quot;1m&quot;呢個concept會越黎越長<br />\n<br />\n樓主講嘅應該係metric expansion, 而我想帶出呢個rate of expansion係慢到唔會感受到，<br />\n(我估)加上係各種單位都expand之下，物理定律得以維持</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我想問光(/電磁波)係咪唔受expansion影響?<br />\n<br />\n其實red shift係基於Doppler effect，因為發光體不斷recede from observer(即係我哋)，導致到我哋接收倒嘅電磁波嘅波長比較長。但以上呢一句嘅假設係當電磁波向我哋呢個方向(向內)travel果陣，唔會被expansion(向外)減慢速度。否則，如果發光體發出嘅電磁波實際上因為expansion嘅緣故而減慢的話，咁啲電磁波就未必會基於Doppler effect而產生red shift。"},{"pid":"448bf43dccb462b6b7b084b09585652b3e8e4bde","tid":788781,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f55c176a1777bcabcc481defa95b013b7f44c990","tid":788781,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"到底數學要去到咩level先睇得明EFE啲term<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"manifold"},{"pid":"a58c18353da48e7909680d2ca9daca80323b2d3e","tid":788781,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc304acb8ba961daf54e23c9536b734296f4eb0","tid":788781,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我岩岩先google 左bound system<br />\nbound system係expansion之下會keep relative position 係因為effect of gravity&gt;expansion<br />\n但expansion of universe 一個key point係metric expension<br />\n即係&quot;1m&quot;呢個concept會越黎越長<br />\n<br />\n樓主講嘅應該係metric expansion, 而我想帶出呢個rate of expansion係慢到唔會感受到，<br />\n(我估)加上係各種單位都expand之下，物理定律得以維持</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我想問光(/電磁波)係咪唔受expansion影響?<br />\n<br />\n其實red shift係基於Doppler effect，因為發光體不斷recede from observer(即係我哋)，導致到我哋接收倒嘅電磁波嘅波長比較長。但以上呢一句嘅假設係當電磁波向我哋呢個方向(向內)travel果陣，唔會被expansion(向外)減慢速度。否則，如果發光體發出嘅電磁波實際上因為expansion嘅緣故而減慢的話，咁啲電磁波就未必會基於Doppler effect而產生red shift。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"Expansion會導致red shift,但唔係 Doppler effect個種<br />\n你可以想象expansion會拉長條光線，令佢wavelength長左"},{"pid":"143fa8e27f76ebecdfc92ea52d53b7dd738b2a25","tid":788781,"uid":101558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n咁我入一粒紅豆落個氣球到<br />\n再吹漲個氣球<br />\n咁粒紅豆係唔係會變大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb277e933fb0e056276203efa00ee76fe2508c0","tid":788781,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"無知一問<br />\n空間膨脹的同時<br />\n星系／星球之間的引力應該會將佢地拉返埋一齊<br />\n即係到最後其實星球之間的距離應該冇變過？"},{"pid":"43c103564a12b88dbf28f35aba7ddb5d2ac8f563","tid":788781,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"衛斯理-狐變<br />\n<br />\n故事講宇宙每一日都會變大一倍既故事"},{"pid":"4fb588bb10a9089165e7bb638593308c9758f98b","tid":788781,"uid":29545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"143fa8e27f76ebecdfc92ea52d53b7dd738b2a25","tid":788781,"uid":101558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n咁我入一粒紅豆落個氣球到<br />\n再吹漲個氣球<br />\n咁粒紅豆係唔係會變大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:34:40.000Z","msg":"咁都俾你破解到 勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face